## Entidades — campos-chave

| Entidade | Campos principais | Módulo |
|---|---|---|
| `account` | id, status, email, passwordHash, role, refreshToken, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 1 |
| `seller` | id, status, name, companyMetaData, legalRepresentativeMetaData, businessRelationsMetaData, accountId, walletId, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 2 |
