| `risk_analyst` | id, status, name, accountId, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 3 |
| `admin` | id, status, name, accountId, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 3 |
| `payer` | id, status, legalName, email, cnpj, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 4 |
| `receivable` | id, status, sellerId, payerId, receivableMetaData, value, proposedValue, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 5 |
| `document` | id, status, parentType, parentId, url, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 6 |
| `registry_on_chain` | id, receivableId, issuerPublicKey, status, payload…, createdAt, updatedAt, confirmedAt, deletedAt | 7 |
| `ramp_quote` | id, userId, provider, externalQuoteId, requestJson, responseJson, expiresAt, status, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 8 |
| `ramp_order` | id, userId, rampQuoteId, externalOrderId, status, requestJson, responseJson, createdAt, updatedAt, deletedAt | 8 |

